claude-sessions

Based on agent-sessions by Vineeth Krishnan (MIT License).
Upstream: https://github.com/vineethkrishnan/agent-sessions
Fork point: main @ initial fork (see git history: upstream/main).

This fork adds tmux orchestration (a persistent "HOME" dashboard, jump-to-live,
resume-in-new-window), liveness detection via .wt-session locks, and integration
with the local worktree tooling (c / set-focus / wtrm). All additions live under
src/domain/rooms/. Upstream code under src/domain/session/ remains under its
original MIT license; see LICENSE.
